# make intellij stop putting underscores in integers
Preferences - Editor - General - Code Folding - SQL - Put underscores inside numeric literals

# stop auto collapsing single line methods
Preferences - Editor - General - Code Folding - Java - One line methods

# make xml files do the sql formatting coolness that humes showed me
Preferences - Editor - Language Injections - new XML Tag Injection - put “sql” into the “Local Name” field and check “Sub-tags”
        Name: whatever, Language ID: Postgres, Local Name: sql  check the sub-tags option

# my custom keymaps:
Build Module: cmd+g
Main Menu - Run - Debug: cmd+shift+d
Tool Windows - Database: cmd+3
Reopen Closed Tab: cmd+shift+T
Move to opposite group: opt+0
Split Vertically: opt+.
Select in Project View: cmd+2

